data.description: In the heart of Coquille is this cozy and unique home with tons of potential! Tucked in a quiet neighborhood that feels secluded. Enjoy the large living room, open kitchen / dining area for entertaining / dinners. Plenty of space, as the basement is used as extra living space. Another perk of this home is a partially covered deck w/ hot tub, perfectly set up for a bqq night! Enjoy your own nice yard with firepit and private little creek. Transform this home into your next dream. By appoitment only. Motivated seller!
